688
00:33:27,533 --> 00:33:31,002
HEY, I WAS JUST THINKING ABOUT YOU.
LOOK AT THIS.

689
00:33:31,036 --> 00:33:34,539
I'VE GOT THESE ADORABLE LITTLE PASTEL
