704
00:34:10,541 --> 00:34:12,341
- I'LL TAKE ONE OF EACH.
- OH.

705
00:34:12,375 --> 00:34:15,010
AND FORGET THE FREEBIE.
BILL TOLD ME TO USE HIS CREDIT CARD

706
00:34:15,044 --> 00:34:17,179
AND BUY WHATEVER I WANT,
NO MATTER WHAT THE PRICE.

707
00:34:17,213 --> 00:34:18,747
WELL, THAT'S REALLY--

