00:34:20,583 --> 00:34:23,018
HE WAS FEELING A LITTLE BIT GUILTY,
WOULDN'T YOU?

710
00:34:23,052 --> 00:34:26,587
OR MAYBE IT'S JUST THAT
HE LOVES ME SO.

711
00:34:26,605 --> 00:34:30,391
UM, COME TO THINK OF IT,
I'LL NEED SOME SHOES

712
00:34:30,425 --> 00:34:33,761
AND, UM, YEAH,
SOME LUGGAGE MAYBE.

713
00:34:33,779 --> 00:34:37,532
YEAH, I MIGHT BE TRAVELING
SOON WITH THE CHILDREN.

714
00:34:37,566 --> 00:34:40,034
