TO BE LEFT HERE ALL ALONE,

715
00:34:40,068 --> 00:34:43,102
BUT I TOLD THE GIRLS WE MIGHT
GO TO TAOS THIS SUMMER.

716
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:45,438
HOW WOULD THAT
WORK FOR YOU?

717
00:34:47,492 --> 00:34:49,626
COULD I SEE YOU
FOR A MINUTE?

718
00:34:58,218 --> 00:35:00,786
WHAT ON EARTH
IS YOUR PROBLEM?

719
00:35:00,804 --> 00:35:04,173
YOU OFFERED TO SHOW ME YOUR
SUNBURNED BACK. DO YOU MIND?

720
00:35:04,224 --> 00:35:06,008
