FOLLOWING YOU AROUND

721
00:35:06,059 --> 00:35:08,511
HAS MADE YOU
A LITTLE NUTS.

722
00:35:08,562 --> 00:35:10,645
ARE YOU COMING
TO THE CONCERT?

723
00:35:10,679 --> 00:35:13,815
I'M NOT SURE
IF I SHOULD.

724
00:35:13,849 --> 00:35:16,935
OH, THE BOYS WOULD BE
HURT IF YOU DIDN'T COME.

725
00:35:16,969 --> 00:35:19,521
WE'VE ALWAYS THOUGHT
OF YOU AS FAMILY, VAL.

726
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:29,496
¶ WE'LL BE FIGHTING
