MADE COPIES
OF OUR TAX FORMS.

1447
01:14:07,855 --> 01:14:09,973
RIGHT.

1448
01:14:13,244 --> 01:14:15,195
AND YOU'VE GOT
THE KIDS

1449
01:14:15,246 --> 01:14:18,781
