what have I done?

1502
01:20:33,515 --> 01:20:36,016
I NEVER WANT TO SEE
THAT MAN AGAIN.

1503
01:20:36,051 --> 01:20:40,019
MOM, I'M--
I'M COMING HOME.

1504
01:20:40,054 --> 01:20:43,189
AND WE'RE GONNA WATCH
THE SHOW WHEN IT AIRS

1505
01:20:43,223 --> 01:20:45,007
TOGETHER, ALL OF US,

1506
01:20:45,025 --> 01:20:47,610
ALL OF US AS A FAMILY.

1507
01:20:47,644 --> 01:20:50,113
They are an American family,

1508
01:20:50,147 --> 01:20:52,115
the family next door
on the surface.

1509
01:20:52,149 --> 01:20:54,232
10 million viewers
watch them every week

1510
01:20:54,283 --> 01:20:56,701
on the most popular,
most watched series

1511
01:20:56,736 --> 01:20:59,071
that educational television
has ever tackled.

1512
01:20:59,122 --> 01:21:02,240
