realize is that

1527
01:21:36,190 --> 01:21:39,057
people were not
going to look at it
as an art form,

1528
01:21:39,075 --> 01:21:41,393
that they were going
to begin criticizing them
as people.

1529
01:21:41,411 --> 01:21:43,112
People dissected
this family

1530
01:21:43,163 --> 01:21:44,746
in order to call
into question

1531
01:21:44,781 --> 01:21:47,616
not only an American family,
but the American family.

1532
01:21:47,667 --> 01:21:49,952
...role as a father, but that
that role was of a pal.

1533
01:21:50,003 --> 01:21:51,753
Have you seen Lance Loud
and that get-up?

1534
01:21:51,788 --> 01:21:53,671
