ON A PERSONAL MISSION.

1541
01:23:01,236 --> 01:23:02,903
COULD THAT EXPLAIN
WHAT WENT WRONG?

1542
01:23:02,937 --> 01:23:05,905
CRAIG DIDN'T SEARCH
FOR THE PERFECT FAMILY.

1543
01:23:05,939 --> 01:23:09,108
HE SEARCHED FOR THE FAMILY
THAT WAS PERFECT FOR HIS AGENDA.

1544
01:23:09,142 --> 01:23:11,027
ANYBODY WANT PIZZA?

1545
01:23:11,078 --> 01:23:13,812
- PIZZA? - OH MY GOD,
I'M AFRAID TO ANSWER IT.

1546
01:23:18,035 --> 01:23:20,336
- HELLO? - HAVE YOU READ
THIS STUFF, PATTY?

1547
01:23:20,370 --> 01:23:22,337
- IT'S YOUR FATHER.
- Get this-- "The father,

1548
01:23:22,371 --> 01:23:24,339
COMPLETELY OUT OF TOUCH
WITH ANY WORLD

1549
01:23:24,373 --> 01:23:26,958
EXCEPT THE FALSE ONE
HE INHABITS, REACHES OUT..."

1550
01:23:26,992 --> 01:23:29,211
WHY DON'T WE INVITE
YOUR DAD TO PIZZA?

1551
01:23:31,013 --> 01:23:32,380
HMM?

1552
01:23:32,415 --> 01:23:34,833
WELL, WE ARE A
CULTURAL PHENOMENON

1553
01:23:34,867 --> 01:23:38,335
AND THE MOST DESPISED
FAMILY IN AMERICA.

1554
01:23:38,353 --> 01:23:40,504
IT'S REALLY ALL TOO
GLAMOROUS TO HANDLE.

1555
01:23:40,522 --> 01:23:42,005
REALLY.
HONESTLY.

1556
01:23:42,023 --> 01:23:44,074
I DON'T WANT
TO BE DESPISED.

1557
01:23:44,109 --> 01:23:47,228
WELL, THEN WE'LL JUST
HAVE TO FIGHT BACK.

1558
01:23:47,279 --> 01:23:49,862
WON'T WE, SWEETHEART?

1559
01:23:58,706 --> 01:24:01,190
"The Dick Cavett Show!"

1560
01:24:02,859 --> 01:24:05,527
WE'RE DOING THIS SHOW
AND A DOZEN OTHERS LIKE IT

1561
01:24:05,545 --> 01:24:07,412
BECAUSE WE WANT
PEOPLE TO KNOW

1562
01:24:07,463 --> 01:24:10,365
THAT WE ARE NOT
MONSTERS OR IDIOTS.

1563
01:24:10,383 --> 01:24:12,417
WE'RE PRETTY
DECENT PEOPLE

1564
01:24:12,468 --> 01:24:14,553
AND DIDN'T REALLY UNDERSTAND
WHAT WE WERE SIGNING UP FOR.

1565
01:24:14,587 --> 01:24:16,805
WE'VE LOST DIGNITY,
AND-- AND--

1566
01:24:16,839 --> 01:24:19,590
AND WE'VE BEEN HUMILIATED
AS A RESULT OF IT.

1567
01:24:19,641 --> 01:24:22,176
OUR HONOR
IS AT QUESTION

1568
01:24:22,210 --> 01:24:24,679
AND I FEEL VERY DEFENSIVE,
AS CRAIG BROUGHT UP.

1569
01:24:24,713 --> 01:24:27,648
PEOPLE HAVE A MUCH DIFFERENT
IMAGE OF THEMSELVES

1570
01:24:27,683 --> 01:24:29,717
THAN SOMETIMES
OTHER PEOPLE HAVE OF THEM.

1571
01:24:29,735 --> 01:24:34,104
I THINK WE'RE MOST HORRIFIED BY THE
THINGS IN OURSELVES THAT WE'RE SCARED OF.

1572
01:24:34,155 --> 01:24:37,524
- WHEN I SAW MYSELF BILLED
AS "HOMO OF THE YEAR 1971..."

1573
01:24:37,558 --> 01:24:39,943
...I WAS REALLY
DESPONDENT FOR A WHILE.

1574
01:24:39,994 --> 01:24:42,862
BUT I KNEW WHAT I WAS GOING
TO COME OFF AS ANYWAY.

1575
01:24:42,896 --> 01:24:44,998
THEY'VE SORT OF
CATEGORIZED US.

1576
01:24:45,032 --> 01:24:47,534
ONE THING IS
THAT YOU BECOME OBLIGED

1577
01:24:47,568 --> 01:24:49,702
UNDER THAT CAMERA
TO REACT IN SOME WAY.

1578
01:24:49,736 --> 01:24:52,171
YOU TRY TO COME UP WITH
SOME PLATO-LIKE DECISION

1579
01:24:52,205 --> 01:24:53,589
WHEN THE CAMERA'S
ROLLING.

1580
01:24:53,623 --> 01:24:55,341
BUT ON THE OTHER HAND,

1581
01:24:55,375 --> 01:24:57,576
ANYBODY WHO'S IN SHOW BUSINESS
WOULD HAVE TO CALL YOU NAIVE

1582
01:24:57,594 --> 01:25:00,045
TO THINK THAT YOU COULD THINK
THAT YOU COULD APPEAR ON TELEVISION

1583
01:25:00,079 --> 01:25:02,014
AND NOT HAVE IT
SELECTED, EDITED.

1584
01:25:02,048 --> 01:25:04,048
I DON'T SEE ANYTHING WRONG
WITH BEING NAIVE.

1585
01:25:04,082 --> 01:25:06,417
I SEE SOMETHING REALLY WRONG
WITH BEING SOPHISTICATED.

1586
01:25:06,435 --> 01:25:09,404
CERTAINLY NO OTHER AMERICAN FAMILY
HAS BEEN THOUGH ANYTHING LIKE THIS.

1587
01:25:09,438 --> 01:25:13,274
THANK YOU FOR BEING HERE AND
BEING SO OUTSPOKEN AND ACCESSIBLE.

1588
01:25:13,309 --> 01:25:15,276
AND WE WILL SEE YOU
TOMORROW NIGHT.

1589
01:25:15,311 --> 01:25:18,061
TO THE LOUDS

1590
01:25:18,095 --> 01:25:20,280
AND OUR 14th MINUTE OF FAME.

1591
01:25:20,315 --> 01:25:22,449
GOOD JOB, EVERYBODY.

1592
01:25:22,483 --> 01:25:25,101
LET'S MILK OUR LAST MINUTE
FOR ALL THAT IT'S WORTH.

1593
01:25:25,119 --> 01:25:27,120
YEAH.

